| **Metric Name**                     | **Definition / Calculation**                                            | **Purpose / Insight**                                       |
| ----------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------- |
| **EncounterID**                     | Unique identifier for each patient encounter                            | Track and analyze individual encounters                     |
| **PatientID**                       | Unique patient identifier                                               | Link encounters to patient history                          |
| **ProviderID**                      | Unique identifier for each provider                                     | Analyze workload and performance per provider               |
| **Department**                      | Clinical department handling the encounter                              | Segment performance by department                           |
| **Shift**                           | Shift during which encounter occurred (e.g., Morning, Evening)          | Shift-level KPI analysis for staffing and throughput        |
| **RegistrationTime**                | Timestamp when patient registered                                       | Start of patient encounter; used in cycle time calculations |
| **TriageTime**                      | Timestamp when patient was triaged                                      | Measure registration-to-triage efficiency                   |
| **ProviderStartTime**               | Timestamp when provider begins encounter                                | Key for patient flow and SLA compliance                     |
| **DocumentationStartTime**          | Timestamp when documentation begins                                     | Monitor documentation process efficiency                    |
| **DocumentationEndTime**            | Timestamp when documentation completes                                  | Track documentation cycle time and compliance               |
| **DischargeTime**                   | Timestamp when patient is discharged                                    | Defines end of encounter for cycle time metrics             |
| **Total_Encounter_Time**            | `DATEDIFF(MINUTE, RegistrationTime, DischargeTime)`                     | Overall encounter efficiency                                |
| **Registration_to_Triage**          | `DATEDIFF(MINUTE, RegistrationTime, TriageTime)`                        | Measures front-end patient flow efficiency                  |
| **Triage_to_Provider**              | `DATEDIFF(MINUTE, TriageTime, ProviderStartTime)`                       | Measures patient waiting time for provider                  |
| **Provider_to_Documentation**       | `DATEDIFF(MINUTE, ProviderStartTime, DocumentationStartTime)`           | Assesses handoff and provider workflow efficiency           |
| **Documentation_Duration**          | `DATEDIFF(MINUTE, DocumentationStartTime, DocumentationEndTime)`        | Time spent on completing documentation                      |
| **SLA_Provider_Start**              | 1 if `ProviderStartTime - RegistrationTime <= 30 mins`, else 0          | Indicates SLA adherence for timely provider start           |
| **SLA_Documentation_Time**          | 1 if `DocumentationEndTime - DocumentationStartTime <= 60 mins`, else 0 | Indicates SLA adherence for documentation completion        |
| **Documentation_Within_24h**        | 1 if documentation completed ≤24 hrs from discharge, else 0             | Ensures timely chart closure for compliance                 |
| **Compliance_Flag**                 | 1 if encounter meets all compliance criteria, else 0                    | Tracks regulatory adherence                                 |
| **Documentation_Rework_Count**      | Number of edits/revisions on documentation                              | Measures workflow inefficiencies and rework                 |
| **Rework_Flag**                     | 1 if `Documentation_Rework_Count > 0`, else 0                           | Highlights encounters requiring rework                      |
| **Provider_Encounter_Count**        | Count of encounters per provider per shift                              | Assesses provider workload and staffing adequacy            |
| **Avg_Encounter_Time_Per_Provider** | Average total encounter time per provider per shift                     | Monitors provider efficiency and workload impact            |
| **Patient_Flow_Within_Target**      | 1 if Registration-to-Provider ≤30 mins, else 0                          | Measures patient flow efficiency                            |
| **Critical_Delay_Flag**             | 1 if high-acuity patient waits beyond safe threshold, else 0            | Identifies potential risk events for intervention           |
